309
00:16:27,680 --> 00:16:29,060
Isn't that the question in middle school?

310
00:16:32,410 --> 00:16:34,860
Slow down. Don't fall down.

311
00:16:53,740 --> 00:16:54,500
Xu Miaomiao.

312
00:16:58,820 --> 00:17:00,240
Bao Jiaguo.

313
00:17:01,570 --> 00:17:03,120
