346
00:18:58,850 --> 00:19:00,170
So,

347
00:19:00,390 --> 00:19:01,380
that cardboard cutout

348
00:19:01,380 --> 00:19:02,700
is our token of love.

349
00:19:03,260 --> 00:19:03,890
Yes.

350
00:19:04,540 --> 00:19:05,630
Then give it to me.

351
