357
00:19:27,430 --> 00:19:28,670
Of course not.

358
00:19:29,670 --> 00:19:31,630
I just leave it in the dorm.

359
00:19:31,660 --> 00:19:33,250
I'll move it to your room another day.

360
00:19:36,560 --> 00:19:37,000
Okay.

361
00:19:44,980 --> 00:19:46,540
