375
00:20:46,260 --> 00:20:47,500
Maybe he just bumped into you.

376
00:20:49,990 --> 00:20:51,390
Actually, I think

377
00:20:51,670 --> 00:20:53,300
Bao Jiaguo is not a bad guy,

378
00:20:53,850 --> 00:20:56,090
