499
00:26:52,850 --> 00:26:53,980
Are you treating?

500
00:26:54,000 --> 00:26:54,870
My treat.

501
00:26:58,680 --> 00:26:59,780
You won the lottery?

502
00:27:01,950 --> 00:27:03,200
